{"tid":1926922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防疫官員呼籲民眾不要用手碰觸嘴巴，下一秒馬上用舌頭舔手","createTime":"2020-03-15T12:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T12:44:57.000Z","uid":188176,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db70dbb9bd595088c4e3ec42cdae796528adb80c","tid":1926922,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uhhY7A38ujE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuhhY7A38ujE&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=d41aea4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uhhY7A38ujE</a><br />\n<br />\n影片中的官員是美國聖克拉拉市公共衛生局的局長Sara Cody，他本身也是一名醫生。<br />\n<br />\n目前美國聖克拉拉市內有11例的確診病例，而近期在美國西岸也新增多起確診病例，且許多患者都不曾到過疫區，也沒有相關旅遊史。此外日前西雅圖更出現了美國境內第一起的死亡病例，這也引起了加州、奧勒岡州和華盛頓州的衛生官員的高度警戒。<br />\n<br />\n根據2015年公布的一項研究，人平均每小時會碰觸自己的臉部23次，而碰觸的區域更高度集中在眼睛、鼻子和嘴巴，也就是病毒進入人體的主要途徑。<br />\n<br />\n對此美國總統川普週三表示，自己已經好幾個禮拜沒有摸臉，更說自己「很想念」那些能摸臉的日子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taisounds.com/w/TaiSounds/society_20030512151198440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taisounds.com%2Fw%2FTaiSounds%2Fsociety_20030512151198440&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=e4f6cd26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.taisounds.com/w/TaiSounds/society_20030512151198440</a>"},{"pid":"60238e5e33ccb0cbbc99c44287e86b93954aa39e","tid":1926922,"uid":346806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"仆街！<br />\n就算平時都唔會咁舔手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><